Package: augere.screen
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2025-11-12
Title: Automatic Generation of Functional Screen Analyses
Description:
    Implements pipelines for generating functional screen analysis reports in the augere framework.
    This uses voom to test for differential abundance of barcodes with consolidation into gene-level statistics.
    Each pipeline function generates a self-contained Rmarkdown report with all of the steps required to reproduce the analysis.
